MOST IMMEDIATE
No.1/34/1/2019-Cab.
GOVERNMENT OF INDIA (BHARAT SARKAR)
CABINET SECRETARIAT (MANTRIMANDAL SACHIVALAYA)
New Delhi, the 23 January, 2019
The undersigned is directed to say that with effect from the 23rd January, 2019:
Shri Arun Jaitley relinquished the charge of the office of the Minister of Finance and the
charge of the office of the Minister of Corporate Affairs. Shri Arun Jaitley assumed the
charge of the office of the Minister without Portfolio during the period of his indisposition
or till such time he is able to resume his work as Minister of Finance and Minister of
Corporate Affairs; and
i)
ii)
Shri Piyush Goyal assumed the charge of the office of the Minister of Finance and the
charge of the office of the Minister of Corporate Affairs temporarily during the period of
indisposition of Shri Arun Jaitley. Shri Piyush Goyal will continue to hold the charge of
the office of the Minister of Railways and the charge of the office of the Minister of Coal.
(Bhaskar Dasgupta)
